data.description: This lakefront home has everything you need to enjoy everything Florida has to offer! This 2019 built DR Horton Cali extended model has it ALL! Situated on the lake, fenced in yard, and also in a cul de sac you have TONS of privacy! Additions to the house include gutters, beautiful landscaping, and an extended patio for your perfect outside oasis. Hook up for permanent generator.  Brand new irrigation with sprayers. Attic is plywood and pulldown ladder was added. Low HOA includes access to gym, pool, & tennis court. New AC with warranty! Schedule your time to view today!
